Preheat the oven to 220C/425F/Gas 7.Place the cheese in a box on a baking sheet and sprinkle with the thyme leaves.Drizzle with olive oil and sprinkle with salt and freshly ground black pepper.Place in the oven and bake for 10-12 minutes, or until just beginning to melt.Remove from the oven and serve on a plate with the chopped pepper pieces and rustic bread pieces beside.